videos.headline: Cooke, Boston lead Gamecocks' steamroll of Buccaneers
videos.description: Zia Cooke scores 16 points as Aliyah Boston records her 67th career double-double as No. 1 South Carolina moves to 11-0 with the 87-23 win over Charleston Southern.
